 "name": "RPlog_Parley_For_Brandis_-_Part_1",
 "title": "Parley for Brandis (Part 1)",
 "summary": "Over the Imperial capital of Selene, the Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin surveys his domain when sensors flag an inbound shuttle and four X-Wings. Aboard the shuttle Tydirium, Luke Skywalker, accompanied by the Chyleni pilot Kyrin Sh'vani and Johanna, draws on the Force as he requests parley with Kreldin for the exchange of the captured Jedi Brandis Finian. Recalling their fraught past, the wary Kreldin grants clearance and orders a heavy guard detail to the hangar even as he extends honors to his old adversary. The two sides converge on the hangar bay, tension thick as Skywalker's delegation prepares to descend into the heart of Imperial power.",
